name: SOULONSOL
description: Soul On Sol ($SOS) was launched for the people of Solana with the goal of creating a trusted and community-meme token. 80% of the supply has been locked and an additional 3.5% was burned via the Solana burn address to protect investors and demonstrate long-term commitment. Soul, the project’s pixel-art character, embodies the degen nature of Solana culture while symbolizing resilience, creativity, and the network’s growth in future years.
